    <item>
      <title>१८ मोक्षयिष्यामि</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/10_pAda-4/18_moxayiShyAmi/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/10_pAda-4/18_moxayiShyAmi/</guid>
      <description>&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;THE MEANING OF THE WORD MOKṢAYIṢYĀMI (I WILL SET THEE FREE)   page595&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Español&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;EL SIGNIFICADO DE LA PALABRA MOKṢAYIṢYĀMI (TE HARÉ LIBRE) página 595&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;इषट-कल&#34;&gt;इष्ट-कालः&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;‘‘मोक्षयिष्यामि’’ ऎऩ्ऱदु&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;उऩक्क् इष्टम् आऩ बोदु&lt;br&gt;&#xA;मुक्तऩ् आक्कुवऩ्&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ऎऩ्ऱ बडि।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;नीलमेघः (सं)&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;(&amp;ldquo;मोक्षयिष्यामि&amp;rdquo; शब्दार्थः)&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;मोक्षयिष्यामि&amp;rdquo; इत्य् अनेनोच्यते,&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;त्वद् इष्ट-समये (त्वां) मुक्तम् आपादयेयम्&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इति ।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The word mokṣayishyami (&amp;lsquo;I will set thee free from all sins&amp;rsquo;) means&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;I will grant thee release (from the bondage of saṁsāra)&lt;br&gt;&#xA;at the time when you &lt;strong&gt;want&lt;/strong&gt; it&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>१९ मा शुचः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/10_pAda-4/19_mA_shuchaH/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/tattvam/venkaTa-nAtha-shAkhA/venkaTanAthaH/rahasya-traya-sAraH/sarva-prastutiH/3_pada-vAkya-yojanA-vibhAgaH/29_charama-shlokAdhikAraH/10_pAda-4/19_mA_shuchaH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;परवश&#34;&gt;प्रवेशः&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;THE MEANING OF ‘MĀ ŚUCHAH’ (DO NOT GRIEVE - DO NOT DESPAIR)  page609&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;Español&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;EL SIGNIFICADO DE ‘MĀ ŚUCHAH’ (&lt;strong&gt;NO TE LLORES - NO DESESPERES&lt;/strong&gt;) página 609&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details open&gt;&lt;summary&gt;विश्वास-प्रस्तुतिः&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इऩि मेल् ‘‘मा शुचः’’ ऎऩ्गिऱव् इत्ताले&lt;br&gt;&#xA;कीऴ् अरुळिच् चॆय्दव् अर्थत्तिल्&lt;br&gt;&#xA;तीर्वु+++(=निश्चयः)+++ प्रकाशितम् आगिऱदु।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;नीलमेघः (सं)&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;इतः परं &amp;ldquo;मा शुचः&amp;rdquo; इत्य् अनेन&#xA;पूर्वोक्तार्थे यत् फलितं&lt;br&gt;&#xA;तत् प्रकाशितं भवति ।&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/details&gt;&#xA;&lt;details&gt;&lt;summary&gt;English&lt;/summary&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Thereafter the words,&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&amp;ldquo;&lt;strong&gt;Do not grieve&lt;/strong&gt;”&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;reveal&lt;/strong&gt; the certainty of what &lt;strong&gt;has been stated&lt;/strong&gt; before.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
